{"tid":1447332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，不如先停阻路，搞超大遊行再文宣推全港罷買日？","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:48:00.000Z","uid":199235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"611153bea05d0a7dda3183e59721a4c30741cdfd","tid":1447332,"uid":199235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:48:00.000Z","msg":"唉，今日睇到軍警政權係唔怕後生仔阻路集會甚至圍狗屋，賤到假扮前線煽動示威者去陷阱圍捕仲要打到爆肛<br />\n你出幾多佢地就打幾多，佢地態度跟本就唔當你係人<br />\n<br />\n但睇到黑警去到邊區都引黎超大民怨<br />\n連太古呢啲中產區都咁多人肯走出黎<br />\n大部份係睇唔過眼黑警咁樣打人<br />\n仲有係亂掟催淚彈影響居民<br />\n<br />\n我相信有惻隱之心既香港人今日見到黑警咁打後生仔，都會肯再上街響應罷買活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢地幾不滿都好，係只敢出聲鬧但唔敢為後生仔擋棍擋子彈<br />\n而黑警只會怕普通既香港市民，因為無得出手<br />\n<br />\n襯而家民怨再次高漲不如食住個勢推用經濟活動比壓力軍警政權啦？見佢地比人咁打真係睇到好心痛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主題反對軍警政府極權治港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}